# kAudioOutputUnitRange

**Global Variable**

The start of the numerical range for I/O audio unit function selectors.

## Declaration

```swift
var kAudioOutputUnitRange: Int { get }
```

## Constants

- **kAudioOutputUnitStartSelect**: Used by the system to start an I/O audio unit when you call the [doc://com.apple.audiotoolbox/documentation/AudioToolbox/AudioOutputUnitStart(_:)] function.
- **kAudioOutputUnitStopSelect**: Used by the system to stop an I/O audio unit when you call the [doc://com.apple.audiotoolbox/documentation/AudioToolbox/AudioOutputUnitStop(_:)] function.
